headline: Corrections & Amplifications
summary: CORRECTIONS A chart showing the S&P 500 price-to-sales ratio was incorrectly labeled as the S&P 500 price/earnings ratio in a graphic with a Page One article on Tuesday about U.S. stocks.  Tennis player Naomi Osaka is a Japanese citizen.
